{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_11_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 負けられない理由",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……今日は間に合ったな。お疲れ様です、莉央さん\nMVの撮影はもうすぐですよね。準備は出来てますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… I made it on time today. Good work‚ Rio-san.\nThe MV shoot is coming up soon‚ right? Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.5666254044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "当然じゃない。そういう{user}さんは\n今日の撮影にはギリギリ間に合ったみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. And you‚ {user}-san—\nIt seems you barely made it in time for today’s shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2533176002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5075778008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、葵のMV撮影の日には、前の仕事が押して\n遅刻したって聞いたわよ、売れっ子マネージャーさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I heard you were late on Aoi’s MV shoot day‚\nbecause your previous job ran long‚ Mr. Popular Manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9923397701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirまでBIG4になったから大忙しですよ\nそういう莉央さんも、ここしばらく忙しかったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re super busy now that LizNoir made it into the BIG4.\nYou’ve been pretty busy yourself lately‚ haven’t you‚ Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8508912405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。あの後すぐ海外ツアーに行って、帰国早々\n新曲のレコーディングがあって、今日はMV撮影でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Right after that‚ we went on an overseas tour‚ and as soon as we got back‚\nwe had recording for the new song‚ and today is the MV shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0087832452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "目指していたBIG4にやっとなれた……って\n感慨にふける暇さえなかったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We finally achieved our goal of making it into the BIG4… but\nI haven’t even had time to feel emotional about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8087832452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5340888341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも新曲のレコーディングとMV撮影が急に入ったのは\nそもそも莉央さん達が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the reason the recording and MV shoot were suddenly scheduled is\nbecause you all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6827154067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるわよ。『Grab the BIG4』で\n私達が披露する予定のない新曲をやったせいなんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. During “Grab the BIG4‚”\nwe performed a new song that wasn’t planned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.402332147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4492252032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そのせいで、リリースを早めることになったのよね\n事前の相談もなく、勝手なことをして悪かったわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of that‚ the release had to be moved up.\nI’m sorry for acting on my own without consulting you first…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6356654804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8809480667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしてませんよ。あの時はああするのが最善だったと\n今なら分かりますから。……あ、壁にかけてある、それ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not bothered. Looking back‚ I understand now\nthat was the best thing to do. …Ah‚ that thing hanging on the wall—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、この衣装ね。えぇ、そうよ\n『Grab the BIG4』で着たステージ衣装よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ this outfit? Yes‚ that’s right.\nIt’s the stage outfit we wore for “Grab the BIG4.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7753383955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5179677963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "もともとは、その後の新曲用に準備を頼んでいたのに\nセミファイナルに間に合わせてくれて、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Originally‚ I asked for it to be made for the new song afterward‚ but\nyou rushed it in time for the semifinals. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9420050622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2580811183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装を決勝トーナメントに間に合わせてくれ、って\n急に言われた時は、焦りましたよ、ほんと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you suddenly said to have this outfit ready for the finals‚\nI really panicked‚ honestly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6984876022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2819353104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "だから悪かったって言ってるでしょ、もう……\nあの時は無茶なこと頼んじゃったって、反省してるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you I’m sorry about that already… come on…\nI regret making such an unreasonable request back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0982403439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2543163618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大体あの時の莉央さん、凄く思い詰めてて\nはたから見ていて心配でしたよ、本当に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were really weighed down at that time‚ Rio-san.\nWatching from the side‚ I was genuinely worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……悪かったわね……葵の不調も\nリズノワの活動方針の迷走も、どうせ全部私が悪いのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… sorry… Aoi’s decline‚\nand LizNoir’s confusion about our direction—it’s all my fault anyway‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2963505747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.2929934186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことは言ってないじゃないですか\n子供みたいにすねないで下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no one said that!\nPlease don’t sulk like a child…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2980497998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9390054069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "なんですって！？　……まぁいいわ\n貴方には、本当に助けられたものね。そう、あの時――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did you say!? …Well‚ never mind.\nYou really did help me. Yes‚ back then—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8814100904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――決勝トーナメント直前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—One day‚ just before the finals tournament",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8748117132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4814773721
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4814773721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……今、なんて言いました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What did you just say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3414717677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "例の新曲の衣装を間に合わせてちょうだい\n来週の決勝トーナメントで着たいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure the new song outfit is ready.\nBecause I want to wear it at next week’s finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0360847159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.6436043662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』を勝ち進むためには\n使える物は全部使う。出し惜しみなんてしてられないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To win at “Grab the BIG4‚”\nI’ll use everything I can. No holding back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2979123372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.8138308129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの気持ちは分かるけど、焦り過ぎです。だって\n『情熱だけで生きてみろ』はまだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your feelings‚ Rio-san‚ but you’re rushing too much.\nBecause “Try Living on Passion Alone” isn’t ready yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.6419406068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "言いたいことは分かってるわ。葵が活動を休止してるし\n振り付けだって、全然合わせられてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand what you’re saying. Aoi’s on hiatus‚\nand the choreography isn’t coordinated at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.6246532761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6500635387
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲を決勝トーナメントに\n間に合わせるのは、どう考えても無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way we can have that song ready\nfor the finals‚ no matter how you think about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2417268328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "衣装だけ間に合わせても、意味なんてない\n……そう言いたいんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just having the outfit ready alone doesn’t mean anything.\n…That’s what you want to say‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.8246532761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.351060923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……その通りです。でも、そこまで分かっていて\nどうして新しい衣装にこだわるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Exactly. But even knowing all that—\nwhy do you insist on the new outfit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "……だからこそ、この衣装を使いたいの\n新しい曲がなくても、衣装だけでも新しくしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s exactly why I want to use this outfit.\nEven without a new song‚ I want the outfit itself to be fresh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.0632010781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.1727150839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "それで、勝てる可能性を少しでも上げられるなら\n私はそうする。なりふり構わずあがいてやる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that can even slightly increase my chances of winning—\nI’ll do it. I’ll struggle with everything I’ve got.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.6632010781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.3965344115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、浅ましい考えでしょ？　笑ってちょうだい\n……それでも私は勝ちたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh‚ a selfish thought‚ right? Go ahead and laugh.\n…Even so‚ I want to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.3965344115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……笑う訳、ないじゃないですか\n勝負に真剣なのは、浅ましいことなんかじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m not laughing.\nTaking the competition seriously isn’t selfish at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.9666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 235.3333337784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、莉央さんが勝ちたいのは――\nBIG4になりたいのは、自分のためだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ your desire to win‚\nand to join the BIG4‚ isn’t just for yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.3333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方にはお見通しね。そう、私は……\nリーダーとして、みんなを高みに導く義務がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You see right through me. Yes‚ I…\nhave the duty‚ as a leader‚ to guide everyone to the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.6293797497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 248.6155832213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私のことを一年も待ってくれた葵に――\n私のパートナーに、報いたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And to Aoi‚ who has waited for me for a whole year—\nI want to repay my partner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.9895956558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら、どんなに無様でもいい\n私の安いプライドなんて、いくらでも捨ててやるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For that‚ I don’t care how clumsy I look.\nI’ll throw away my petty pride as much as needed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.2627273246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.5079787176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
