      "text": "（……今の莉央さんは、一番信頼するパートナー）\n（――葵との間に距離が出来て、苦しんでいる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Right now‚ Rio-san is struggling with the distance）\n（between herself and Aoi‚ her most trusted partner.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.9160587453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.2834368628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（それでもなお、過酷な決勝トーナメントに）\n（挑もうとする莉央さんに、俺が出来ることは――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…And yet‚ what I can do for Rio-san‚）\n（who’s still facing the grueling finals tournament—）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.1666813533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 279.9094990653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "……お願いよ、{user}さん\n無茶なことを言っているのは、よく分かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Please‚ {user}-san.\nI know I’m asking something unreasonable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.415676785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、頼るしかないの。新しい衣装という\nかすかな希望に……そして、貴方に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have no choice but to rely on that faint hope—\nthe new outfit… and you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.1823434517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 292.2260658113
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 294.9428826255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……無理です。今からじゃ、どうあがいても\n決勝トーナメントの初戦には間に合いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s impossible. No matter what we do now—\nwe won’t make it in time for the first match of the finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.8003296629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "……そう。貴方が言うなら、絶対に無理なのよね\nごめんなさい、わがままを言って。今のは忘れて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. If you say so‚ then it really is impossible.\nI’m sorry for being selfish. Forget what I just said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.7289524047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 312.5855320535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、トーナメントの途中――セミファイナルなら\n間に合うかもしれない……いえ、間に合わせてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But maybe during the tournament—if it’s the semifinals—\nwe could make it in time… no‚ I’ll make sure it is ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.2666630428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 321.5032401962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？　本当に……？\nありがとう。あと、無理をさせてしまってごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Really…?\nThank you. And I’m sorry for making you overwork.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.0415040658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "貴方に約束する。私達LizNoirは\n絶対にセミファイナルまで勝ち上がってみせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I promise you. We‚ LizNoir‚\nwill definitely advance to the semifinals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.6415020312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 338.4561636212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "負けちゃったら、貴方の頑張りを無駄にしちゃうもの\nますます負けられない理由が出来たわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we lose‚ all your effort will be wasted.\nThat just gives us even more reason not to lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.9748353646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。だからセミファイナルまで勝ち進んで下さい\n俺も、万全の状態で衣装を用意しておきますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly. So go ahead and win up to the semifinals.\nI’ll also prepare the outfit in perfect condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.7999963761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
